  "notes": "0.1.38: friend-accept bugfix discovered by multi-client integration tests. The accept SQL was double-quoting 'accepted' which SQLite parses as a column identifier, so accepts errored 500 on the server. Plus friendshipRow now returns status:'mutual' instead of 'accepted' — the renderer was checking for 'mutual' all along. Both fixes are server-side; redeploy server.js to take effect."
